fields.value: Census of population and housing, 1970 summary statistic file 3

dsDescriptionValue.value:
The data for the third count file consists of 38 tables containing 250 population and housing data cells. Population items that are cross- tabulated include race and sex, age and sex, etc. Housing items cross- tabulated include families by plumbing facilities, population in units with 1.01 or more persons per room by tenure and race of head, etc.

Summaries are provided for census blocks in urbanized areas and also areas where blocks were identified on a contractual basis. Census tract s ummaries are provided for that portion containing blocks.

Data contained in the files pertain to the date of the census, April 1, 1970
